ac90d7e7-3780-45c0-a697-20dd1b22f12d	CAU/MG – Conselho de Arquitetura e Urbanismo de Minas Gerais	Edwiges Leal, Danila Ferreira, Marco Antônio Nieves Cardoso, Lucas Lima Leonel Fonseca	duleal@belarq.com.br	URBAN AND LANDSCAPE REDEVELOPMENT OF NICOLAU CESARINO AVENUE AND CONSTRUCTION OF NEW GATEWAYS - EXTREMA MUNICIPALITY	PLANNED	APPROVED	SECTION_V	Extrema	Brazil	-22.8561	-46.319	The project will revitalize Nicolau Cesarino Avenue, Extrema’s main gateway, transforming it from a highway into an urban boulevard prioritizing pedestrians, cyclists, and public transit. It features widened sidewalks, dedicated bike lanes, upgraded drainage, sustainable lighting, and native landscaping, complemented by architectural gateways reflecting Minas Gerais’ heritage. A linear park along the Jaguary River will integrate leisure spaces, dining venues, and local commerce to enhance tourism and community life. By reducing heavy industrial presence near the urban core, the initiative supports small businesses and cultural activities, reinforcing local identity while advancing socio-environmental sustainability.	The project will revitalize Nicolau Cesarino Avenue, Extrema’s main gateway, transforming it from a highway into an urban boulevard prioritizing pedestrians, cyclists, and public transit. It features widened sidewalks, dedicated bike lanes, upgraded drainage, sustainable lighting, and native landscaping, complemented by architectural gateways reflecting Minas Gerais’ heritage. A linear park along the Jaguary River will integrate leisure spaces, dining venues, and local commerce to enhance tourism and community life. By reducing heavy industrial presence near the urban core, the initiative supports small businesses and cultural activities, reinforcing local identity while advancing socio-environmental sustainability.	See detailed description	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	2026-04-18 13:00:15.086189	2026-04-18 13:00:15.086189	P88	Edwiges Leal, Danila Ferreira, Marco Antônio Nieves Cardoso, Lucas Li