maglev entrances and exits in the transfer passage, forming a new transfer corridor can promote the hub to be more humanized.	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	2026-03-01 19:41:05.683573	2026-03-01 19:41:05.683573	IFF28	Shanghai Lab, Tongji University	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
