de82d857-8e58-47d8-bae1-5925f6fba88a	Natureza Urbana	Breno	breno@naturezaurbana.net	Altar Ninho	IMPLEMENTED	SUBMITTED	SECTION_V	Joanópolis	Brazil	-22.9253	-46.2697	Ninho is a retreat created by Altar and Natureza Urbana, aligned with the concept of decentralized, sustainable hotels connected to nature. Located in Joanópolis-SP, the house is elevated up to 4 meters above ground, evoking a treehouse and offering views of the reservoir. Within 20 m², it integrates living, kitchen, and sleeping areas, alongside a bathroom with zenithal lighting and an outdoor deck with leisure space. The project features prefabrication, simple materials, and low-impact solutions, fostering well-being and immersion. Guided by Regenerative Design principles, it embraces the territory as a living system and proposes architecture integrated with its surroundings.	Ninho is a retreat created by Altar and Natureza Urbana, aligned with the concept of decentralized, sustainable hotels connected to nature. Located in Joanópolis-SP, the house is elevated up to 4 meters above ground, evoking a treehouse and offering views of the reservoir. Within 20 m², it integrates living, kitchen, and sleeping areas, alongside a bathroom with zenithal lighting and an outdoor deck with leisure space. The project features prefabrication, simple materials, and low-impact solutions, fostering well-being and immersion. Guided by Regenerative Design principles, it embraces the territory as a living system and proposes architecture integrated with its surroundings.	See detailed description	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	2026-04-18 12:59:53.078529	2026-04-18 12:59:53.078529	P13	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
